data.description: Reduced!!!Welcome to Historic Reservoir Hill with a stunning example of a modern renovation. This newly renovated home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The sellers of this home left no stone unturned and provided modern convenience with an open floor plan which facilitates conversation and socializing.  With easy access to I83, Station North and Druid Hill Park this gem just won't last.
